        <mxCell id="8U9ICg_snljmnY2mWMtf-18" parent="1" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;" value="You don&#39;t need a large block of time. Even 10 minutes at a time counts. Three short walks during your day add up the same as one long session." vertex="1">
